      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/sci-fi/sf-03.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "云朵信号带里漂着软软的云桥，三条航线在空中交会。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是云朵信号带。我们先把“跟随航线”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我听到光核在轻轻嗡鸣，信号就在附近。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先看清蓝色航线，再做一个安全的小动作。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "route",
          "prompt": "让飞船沿着闪烁的云灯前进。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "跟着蓝云灯",
              "feedback": "飞船穿过云桥，找到了下一颗光点。"
            },
            {
              "label": "追着彩虹云",
              "feedback": "彩虹云送来一阵风，把我们吹回了航线。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，跟着蓝云灯让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "扫描光点后，隐藏的星尘轨迹露出来了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这条轨迹和星图接起来，下一站就会亮起。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这束光，它会带我们穿过下一段星际航线。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "原来‘云’会把信号送到很远的地方。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        }
      ],
